{
  "stem": "10970.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, like I said, my uncle was from the same school as my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My, my uncle was an ordained rabbi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a total escape from religion, which came back to him as he grew older.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he would--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My Uncle Gabriel in Paris.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, who I was living with-- had the same feelings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Poland.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he had, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But while I was in England with my cousin Stella and my-- my Uncle Leon was the same thing in London, not religious.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But his daughter, Stella, really became religious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I got a good basis there from the summers and going to temple, and, you know, having Shabbos, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] seeing Jewish religion and going to-- being observant.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And usually I was there for the holidays.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'd go to temple.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was forced to fast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it's fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] When I turned 13 they said, you had to fast.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so I got my Jewish education, basically, more from my cousin in London than from any of my two uncles.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, oh yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, definitely, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- I, I mean, from 11 on-- I-- no, 12 on-- I was going to England by myself from Paris.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'd be on the train in Paris and get off the train, get on the boat, cross the channel, get back on the train to go to London.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were waiting for me at the station, yes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And same back in-- same in reverse, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name is Philip Fiol.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And like I said, we met on Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] quick courtship, I guess, in today's--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was in the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
